<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>一个八方环绕着四季青翠的山水</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">——遂昌。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201023/72e9b679188643998d5ad610fea8beda.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>一个每天早上睁开眼睛，到处都是绿的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">——缙云。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201023/2962836f512e443a92682aeaffd9ab7a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
